The Candle Spell
----------------
To undo the effects of the spell mentioned on the previous page, magicians
can conjure up a magical candle, which sheds light on the environment.
Hin Warriors know how to cast this routine spell, but the success of the
spell determines how long the magical candle will stay in effect.

To cast the spell, one needs the fire-gem, which is lost in the process of
casting. The success of the spell depends on the conjuration and fire skills
of the spellcaster.

Cast this spell by doing:           "candle"
